openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: '1.0'
  title: PetScan
  description: A powerful querying tool for Wikimedia
servers:
  - url: 'https://petscan.wmflabs.org/'
  - url: 'https://cors-anywhere.herokuapp.com/https://petscan.wmflabs.org/'
paths:
  /:
    get:
      summary: Queries Wikimedia
      parameters:
        - name: language
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: project
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: depth
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: categories
          in: query
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: string
        - name: combination
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - subset
              - union
        - name: negcats
          in: query
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: string
        - name: 'ns[0]'
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: 'ns[6]'
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: larger
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: smaller
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: since_rev0
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: minlinks
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: maxlinks
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string

          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: after
          in: query

            type: string

          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: show_redirects
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: show_soft_redirects
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: show_disambiguation_pages
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: 'edits[bots]'
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: 'edits[anons]'
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: 'edits[flagged]'
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: page_image
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: ores_type
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: ores_prob_from
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: ores_prob_to

        - name: links_to_any

            type: string
        - name: links_to_no
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string

          in: query

          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - html
              - csv
              - tsv
              - wiki
              - json
              - pagepile
              - plain
        - name: output_compatability
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - catscan
              - quick-intersection
        - name: sortby
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string

              - none
              - title
              - ns_title
              - size
              - date
              - incoming_links
              - filesize
              - uploaddate
              - sitelinks
              - random
              - defaultsort
        - name: sortorder
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string

              - ascending
              - descending
        - name: regexp_filter
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: min_redlink_count
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: output_limit
          in: query
          schema:
            type: integer
        - name: referrer_url
          in: query

            type: string
        - name: referrer_name
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: sparse
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: json-pretty
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: doit
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
            enum:
              - true
      responses:

          description: ''
